  <source>Jessa Hospital</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The usability, skin reactions and accuracy of the FreeStyle Libre glucose monitoring system
      in children will be evaluated by questionnaires, pictures of the insertion site and
      comparison of the glucose results with capillary blood glucose determinations.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
